{"author":"Joe Oakhart","author_email":"joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com","author_id":"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d","author_sig":"{\"payload\": \"\", \"payloadType\": \"application/vnd.rebar.authorship.v1+json\", \"signatures\": [{\"keyid\": \"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d\", \"sig\": \"\"}]}","data":{"content_hash":"1f056112a3933fb1e3b48402945b7152c8a03cfe451a7eba6240af2b7091c00d","digest":{"component_or_area":"provider config scaffolding and CLAUDE.md-to-AGENTS.md reference migration","key_entities":["AGENTS.md","CLAUDE.md",".codex/config.toml",".agents/rules/rebar.md","docs/plan-review-criteria-guide.md","src/rebar/llm/plan_review/criteria_routing.json","src/rebar/llm/reviewers/plan_review_T5e.md","src/rebar/reducer/_processors.py","CHANGELOG.md","docs/event-schema.md",".github/copilot-instructions.md",".cursor/rules","git grep","git ls-files"],"problem_keywords":["reference sweep","migration","provider config","version control","untracked files","git-excluded","canonical guidance","per-tool pointers","documentation rename"],"propositions":["Tracked-file references to CLAUDE.md across ~17 owned files must be retargeted to AGENTS.md or the new docs home.","The provider config .codex/config.toml is locally git-excluded and untracked, so no other clone or provider sees it; it must be committed pointing at AGENTS.md.","A concise .agents/rules/rebar.md must be committed that references AGENTS.md as the source of truth, since Antigravity rules do not support @-imports.","CHANGELOG.md CLAUDE.md hits are deliberately left unchanged as historical record, and docs/event-schema.md and examples are owned by other stories.","The per-tool-pointer decision (Copilot, Cursor, Gemini configs) is deferred to a follow-up with none added in this story.","All prose CLAUDE.md references are comments so the rename breaks zero code, and CLAUDE_CODE_SESSION_ID must not be matched by the sweep."]},"digest_hash_version":1,"model":"claude-opus-4-8","schema":"ticket_digest_v1"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c098